## Allow user to run the Tor Control Panel firewall helper without a password
## This is required to allow the GUI (running as user) to modify
## specific nftables rules for the Exit Proxy feature.

%sudo ALL=(root) NOPASSWD: /usr/libexec/tor-control-panel/tcp-firewall-helper
